---
// Candle Master - Privacy Policy Page
const appName = 'Candle Master';
const appUrl = 'https://app.candlemaster.app';
const siteUrl = 'https://candlemaster.app';
const contactEmail = 'pathofmeow.dev@gmail.com';
const lastUpdated = 'February 10, 2026';
---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="32x32" href="/favicon-32.png" />
    <link rel="icon" href="/favicon.ico" sizes="32x32" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />

    <!-- SEO Meta Tags -->
    <title>Privacy Policy — {appName}</title>
    <meta name="description" content="Privacy Policy for Candle Master trading simulator game. Learn how we collect, use, and protect your data." />

    <!-- Canonical -->
    <link rel="canonical" href={`${siteUrl}/privacy`} />

    <!-- Geist Font -->
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://cdn.vercel.com" crossorigin />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.vercel.com/geist/font/sans/geist-sans.css" />

    <!-- Theme CSS -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/theme.css" />
  </head>

  <body>
    <main class="legal-page">
      <div class="legal-container">
        <!-- Back to Home -->
        <a href="/" class="back-link">← Back to Home</a>

        <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p class="last-updated">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>

        <section>
          <h2>1. Introduction</h2>
          <p>
            {appName} ("we", "our", or "us") operates the {appName} mobile application and website
            (the "Service"). This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard
            your information when you use our Service.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2>2. Information We Collect</h2>

          <h3>2.1 Information You Provide</h3>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Account Information:</strong> When you sign in with Google, we receive your name, email address, and profile picture from your Google account.</li>
            <li><strong>Subscription Information:</strong> When you purchase a PRO subscription, payment is processed by Stripe (for web) or Apple/Google (for native apps). We do not store your credit card or payment details directly.</li>
          </ul>

          <h3>2.2 Information Collected Automatically</h3>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Usage Data:</strong> Game statistics, trading history within the app, and feature usage patterns.</li>
            <li><strong>Device Information:</strong> Device type, operating system, and browser type for compatibility purposes.</li>
          </ul>

          <h3>2.3 Information We Do NOT Collect</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Real financial or brokerage account information</li>
            <li>Credit card numbers (handled by Stripe/Apple/Google)</li>
            <li>Location data</li>
            <li>Contact lists or phone data</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2>3. How We Use Your Information</h2>
          <ul>
            <li>To provide and maintain the Service</li>
            <li>To manage your account and subscription status</li>
            <li>To save your game progress and statistics</li>
            <li>To communicate with you about the Service (e.g., updates, support)</li>
            <li>To improve and optimize the Service</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2>4. Third-Party Services</h2>
          <p>We use the following third-party services:</p>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Firebase (Google):</strong> Authentication and user management</li>
            <li><strong>Stripe:</strong> Payment processing for web subscriptions</li>
            <li><strong>Apple App Store / Google Play:</strong> Payment processing for native app subscriptions</li>
            <li><strong>Cloudflare:</strong> Hosting and content delivery</li>
          </ul>
          <p>Each third-party service has its own privacy policy governing the use of your information.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2>5. Data Storage and Security</h2>
          <p>
            Your game data is stored locally on your device using browser storage (localStorage).
            Account and subscription data is stored securely using Firebase and Cloudflare infrastructure.
            We implement appropriate security measures to protect your personal information.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2>6. Data Retention</h2>
          <p>
            We retain your account information for as long as your account is active. Game data stored
            locally on your device can be cleared at any time. If you wish to delete your account,
            please contact us at <a href={`mailto:${contactEmail}`}>{contactEmail}</a>.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2>7. Children's Privacy</h2>
          <p>
            Our Service is not intended for children under 13. We do not knowingly collect personal
            information from children under 13. If you believe we have collected information from a
            child under 13, please contact us immediately.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2>8. Your Rights</h2>
          <p>You have the right to:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Access the personal data we hold about you</li>
            <li>Request correction of inaccurate data</li>
            <li>Request deletion of your data</li>
            <li>Withdraw consent for data processing</li>
            <li>Export your data in a portable format</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2>9. Changes to This Policy</h2>
          <p>
            We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes
            by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page and updating the "Last updated" date.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2>10. Contact Us</h2>
          <p>
            If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at:
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li>Email: <a href={`mailto:${contactEmail}`}>{contactEmail}</a></li>
            <li>Website: <a href={siteUrl}>{siteUrl}</a></li>
          </ul>
        </section>
      </div>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>

<style>
  .legal-page {
    min-height: 100vh;
    background: var(--bg-primary);
    padding: 2rem 1.5rem 4rem;
  }

  .legal-container {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .back-link {
    display: inline-block;
    color: var(--accent-primary);
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    transition: opacity 0.2s;
  }

  .back-link:hover {
    opacity: 0.8;
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 2.5rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .last-updated {
    color: var(--text-tertiary);
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  section {
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    padding: 0;
  }

  h2 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-default);
  }

  h3 {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin: 1.25rem 0 0.75rem;
  }

  p {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  ul {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.8;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  li {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  a {
    color: var(--accent-primary);
  }

  a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  strong {
    color: var(--text-primary);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .legal-page {
      padding: 1.5rem 1rem 3rem;
    }
  }
</style>
